  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503400/extras/74d8753b4d98622a6439b4393201ebd4.poster.avif?t=1769095185\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503400/extras/74d8753b4d98622a6439b4393201ebd4.webm?t=1769095185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503400/extras/74d8753b4d98622a6439b4393201ebd4.mp4?t=1769095185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Temporal Purge: Z is a wave-based, single-player zombie survival FPS. Travel to various locations throughout space and time, searching for a cure for the plague that has ravaged all human life. With an ever-expanding choice of weapons and maps, leaderboards to climb, and secrets to uncover, Temporal Purge: Z is infinitely replayable. </strong>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Command your own spaceship and harness interdimensional portals<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503400/extras/3be4fcbe2dbf379b998056726ec46691.poster.avif?t=1769095185\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503400/extras/3be4fcbe2dbf379b998056726ec46691.webm?t=1769095185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503400/extras/3be4fcbe2dbf379b998056726ec46691.mp4?t=1769095185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Control mysterious cosmic powers to upgrade your weapons.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503400/extras/dbce97f0b028789f7685a6268ec572fb.poster.avif?t=1769095185\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503400/extras/dbce97f0b028789f7685a6268ec572fb.webm?t=1769095185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503400/extras/dbce97f0b028789f7685a6268ec572fb.mp4?t=1769095185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503400/extras/74d8753b4d98622a6439b4393201ebd4.poster.avif?t=1769095185\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503400/extras/74d8753b4d98622a6439b4393201ebd4.webm?t=1769095185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503400/extras/74d8753b4d98622a6439b4393201ebd4.mp4?t=1769095185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Temporal Purge: Z is a wave-based, single-player zombie survival FPS. Travel to various locations throughout space and time, searching for a cure for the plague that has ravaged all human life. With an ever-expanding choice of weapons and maps, leaderboards to climb, and secrets to uncover, Temporal Purge: Z is infinitely replayable. </strong>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Command your own spaceship and harness interdimensional portals<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503400/extras/3be4fcbe2dbf379b998056726ec46691.poster.avif?t=1769095185\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503400/extras/3be4fcbe2dbf379b998056726ec46691.webm?t=1769095185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503400/extras/3be4fcbe2dbf379b998056726ec46691.mp4?t=1769095185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Control mysterious cosmic powers to upgrade your weapons.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503400/extras/dbce97f0b028789f7685a6268ec572fb.poster.avif?t=1769095185\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503400/extras/dbce97f0b028789f7685a6268ec572fb.webm?t=1769095185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503400/extras/dbce97f0b028789f7685a6268ec572fb.mp4?t=1769095185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>",
